Package: trps
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Trophic Position Models using 'Stan'
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Benjamin L.", "Hlina",
      email = "benjamin.hlina@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Bayesian trophic position models using 'stan' by leveraging 'brms' for 
             stable isotope data. Trophic position models are derived by using 
             equations from 
             Post (2002) <doi:10.1890/0012-9658(2002)083[0703:USITET]2.0.CO;2>,
             Vander Zanden and Vadeboncoeur (2002) <doi:10.1890/0012-9658(2002)083[2152:FAIOBA]2.0.CO;2>, 
             and 
             Heuvel et al. (2024) <doi:10.1139/cjfas-2024-0028>. 
